<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hospital Loayza - Sistema de Gestión</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">


    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">


    <!-- Bootstrap JS (al final del body) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #0066cc !important;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.2);
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fff !important;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: #fff !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #e3f2fd !important;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.8), rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.8)), url('/wwwroot/img/Hospital_Imgaen.jpg') no-repeat center/cover;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .card {
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 1500px;
            background: #fff;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .card-header {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            padding: 0 0 20px 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            border-color: #0066cc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background-color: #004c99;
            border-color: #004c99;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .quick-access-grid, .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .quick-access-item, .service-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .quick-access-item:hover, .service-item:hover {
            background: #e3f2fd;
        }

        .quick-access-item i, .service-item i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #0066cc;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .quick-access-item a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: block;
        }

        .quick-access-item a:hover {
            color: #004c99;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .news-carousel .carousel-item {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .news-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .news-item i {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #28a745;
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .contact-item i {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>


    
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1><i class="bi bi-heart-pulse-fill"></i> Bienvenido al Sistema de Gestión de Pacientes del Hospital Arzobispo Loayza</h1>
            <p>Optimiza la atención en el Hospital Nacional Arzobispo Loayza. Registra pacientes, gestiona citas y genera reportes de manera eficiente y segura.</p>
            <a asp-controller="Pacientes" asp-action="RegistrarPaciente" class="btn btn-primary-custom">Registrar Nuevo Paciente</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <main class="container">
        
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2><i class="bi bi-speedometer2"></i> Accesos Rápidos</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="quick-access-grid">
                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-fill"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="Medicos" asp-action="ListaMedicos">Ver Lista de Medicos</a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-bar-graph"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="Reporte" asp-action="GenerarReporte">Generar Reporte</a>
                </div>
                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-calendar-check-fill"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="HorariosMedicos" asp-action="ListaHorariosMedicos">Ver Lista de Horarios Medicos</a>
                </div>
                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-lines-fill"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="Pacientes" asp-action="ListaPacientes">Ver Lista de Pacientes</a>
                </div>
                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="CitasMedicas" asp-action="ListaCitasMedicas">Ver Lista de Citas Médicas</a>
                </div>

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-gear-fill"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="Medicos" asp-action="ListaMedicos">Gestionar Médicos</a>
                </div>

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-journal-medical"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="CitasMedicas" asp-action="RegistrarCitaPaciente">Registrar Cita Médica</a>
                </div>

                

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-clock-fill"></i>
                        <a asp-controller="HorariosMedicos" asp-action="ListaHorariosMedicos">Gestionar Horarios Médicos</a>
                </div>

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-person-fill"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="Pacientes" asp-action="ListaPacientes">Gestionar Pacientes</a>
                </div>

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-calendar2-check-fill"></i>
                    <a asp-controller="CitasMedicas" asp-action="ListaCitasMedicas">Gestionar Citas Médicas</a>
                </div>

                

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-person-badge-fill"></i>
                        <a asp-controller="Medicos" asp-action="RegistrarMedico">Registrar Nuevo Médico</a>
                </div>

                <div class="quick-access-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-calendar-plus-fill"></i>
                        <a asp-controller="HorariosMedicos" asp-action="RegistrarHorarioMedico">Registrar Nuevo Horario Médico</a>
                </div>

    
                
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2><i class="bi bi-newspaper"></i> Noticias y Avisos</h2>
            </div>
            <div id="newsCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <div class="news-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-pin-angle-fill"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Campaña de Vacunación:</strong> Este sábado se atenderá gratuitamente a niños menores de 5 años en el pabellón principal.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="news-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-person-heart"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Nuevo Especialista:</strong> El Dr. Pérez se une al área de Cardiología para mejorar nuestra atención cardiovascular.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="news-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Aviso Importante:</strong> Por mantenimiento, el laboratorio clínico estará cerrado este domingo. Disculpen las molestias.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="news-item">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Actualización del Sistema:</strong> Nueva funcionalidad para notificaciones push en citas médicas.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#newsCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Anterior</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#newsCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="visually-hidden">Siguiente</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2><i class="bi bi-list-check"></i> Servicios Destacados</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-heart-fill"></i>
                    <div>Medicina General</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="service-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-droplet-half"></i>
                    <div>Laboratorio Clínico</div>
                </div>
                <div class="service-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-house-heart"></i>
                    <div>Emergencias</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2><i class="bi bi-telephone"></i> Contacto Rápido</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-telephone-fill"></i>
                    <strong>(01) 509-4800</strong> - Central Telefónica
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill"></i>
                    Av. Alfonso Ugarte 848, Lima 15082
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-envelope-fill"></i>
                    <a href="mailto:info@hospital.com" style="color: #0066cc;">mesadepartes@hospitalloayza.gob.pe</a>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="bi bi-clock-fill"></i>
                    Horario: Lunes a Viernes, 8:00 - 20:00
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>





</body>
</html>
